lead_paragraph: Diamond DeShields scored 15 points and Tennessee beat No. 10 Stanford 59-51 on Sunday to snap the Cardinal's six-game winning streak.

headline.print_headline: Lady Vols Knock Off No. 10 Stanford 59-51
